        "formTitle": "Automated Newsletter Agent",
        "formDescription": "An intelligent n8n workflow that automates the creation and delivery of newsletters. It collects content from multiple sources such as RSS feeds, emails, or databases, curates and formats it, and distributes personalized updates to subscribers on a schedule. This agent streamlines communication, reduces manual effort, and ensures timely, relevant content reaches the audience consistently.",
